        "text": "Tyler is a great photographer and an even better person! He's communication was impeccable and the photos he took are some photos my fiancé and I will cherish forever! Thank you for everything you do Tyler!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2021-01",
        "text": "I absolutely love Tyler’s work and was so excited to get couples photos done with him! He is professional and I had so much fun getting creative in the outdoors with my boyfriend. His editing style is so unique and my friends love the images he created for us! If you’re looking for one of a kind prints that stand out from every other couples shoot and a fun experience I highly recommend Tyler!! I strongly suggest taking advantage of his travel experience and traveling somewhere unique for your photos. He will literally take you across the globe if your willing, why not! 10/10 Experience and photos"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2020-12",
        "text": "Tyler is by far the most creative photographer in the game! If you want one of a kind images that blow your mind, Tyler is the photographer for you. No matter if it’s wedding or couple photos, action shots, landscape, or anything in between, he has an incredible eye for lighting, creative angles and one of a kind images. His editing process will leave you in awe and leave you with the most beautiful and long lasting memories. The way he captured sunrises, sunsets and the sky is breathtaking. You will not regret working with Tyler. One of the most innovative photographers out there! And his prices are literally impossible to beat for the quality!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2020-12",
        "text": "Tyler is a one of a kind photographer. His passion and creativity is unmatched. We loved our engagement shoot so much that we flew him out to Hawaii to shoot our wedding! And of course we were not disappointed. I have shot with many photographers and he is by far my favorite. If I could give more stars I would! Thank you Tyler!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2020-12",
        "text": "Tyler came to Montana and took engagement pictures of my fiance and I. He is very professional, and you can see the passion that he has for taking pictures. My fiance and I are older, yet he was able to capture a much younger, playful side to both of us. He also took pictures of my fiance's 13-year-old son. I have to say they're the best pictures I've ever seen of Moses. He captured the horses on our ranch and showed their wild side, but also the soft gentle hearts that they all have. I would recommend Tyler to any and every person that is looking for someone to take more than a photograph, he will give something to you that you will cherish for a lifetime and will be passed down for years to come."
      }
